title: Amiga music: Jochen Hippel - The Seven Gates of Jambala full OST (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:
"The Seven Gates of Jambala" (Amiga, 1989) full soundtrack by Jochen Hippel.

00:00 Thalion intro
02:29 Thalion intro 2
04:45 Title 1
09:03 Title 2
13:10 Outdoors
15:51 Level 1
18:38 Level 2
21:22 Level 3
24:15 Level 4
26:19 Level 5
28:34 Level 6
30:33 Level 7
33:01 Bosses
35:08 Ending
38:12 Highscore

Couple of questions:

- Title 2, when is this heard in the game? Game opens with the first title.
- The second Thalion intro, how can you get it to play? I always hear the first one and it just loops over and over.

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio. Mostly utilizing SOG_SevenGatesOfJambala.lzx from The Wanted Team (http://wt.exotica.org.uk/examples.html). Playback from DeliTracker.

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
